lead_paragraph: Bulgaria have appointed Petar Hubchev as their new coach to replace Ivaylo Petev, who is set to take over at Croatian champions Dinamo Zagreb, the Bulgarian Football Union (BFU) said on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Bulgaria Name Hubchev as Coach to Replace Petev
